episodes.title: My Experience being indoctrinated into the MAGA Cult...
episodes.description:
I wanted to recount my experience of growing up being indoctrinated into the MAGA cult and the lifelong effects it had on me. This is different than my typical reptile education videos on my main channel; I'd like to keep away from politics or sensitive topics there if possible. Regardless, I still wanted to share this, even if only a handful of people see it. Thanks for watching!

Perfectly timed for the 4th of July, Happy Birthday America. Let's do better, 8647!
